titleInfo.title: M&M Communications v. Telephone Management
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM AND ORDER-Parties are directedTMC is orde to promptly negotiate a mutally acceptable confidentiality agreement; upon negotiation of a mutually acceptable confidentiality agreement, red to respond to M&M's written discovery requests within thirty days; upon negotiation of a mutually acceptable confidentiality agreement, TMC is ordered to respond to M&M's request for production of documents by making all documents and records available for inspection by M&M at TMC's Portland, Oregon, offices; M&M and TMC are both ordered to make their respective corporate designees available for deposition prior to August 15, 2005; TMC may not schedule the deposition of M&M's corporate designee until TMC has complied with M&M's discovery requests by providing answers to written discovery and M&M has completed its inspection of TMC's records at TMC's Portland offices. Signed by Judge Lyle E. Strom on 5/2/2005. (MKR, )
